title: Re-entry capsule of Shenzhou-8 set to land on earth Thursday evening
description: BEIJING， Nov. 16 (Xinhua) -- The re-entry capsule of China's unmanned spacecraft Shenzhou-8 is set to land back on earth at around 7 p.m. Thursday Beijing time， a spokesperson for China's manned space program said Wednesday.
